With a committee management module, organizations can streamline their committee processes and reduce administrative overhead. The Committee Management module will assist privileged to users to manage all features related to committees including features such as Committee creation, editing, deleting, requesting new members, listing and details pages, etc. The committee management module will serve as a common component that can be used by other modules that need a
